item.description:

All Silabsoft servers actually aren’t a very good source to use. I would rather make your own items, your own client, or have no skillcapes, godswords etc. This one doesn’t look very good as any others.

My suggestions
[hr]
Remove the PK box.
Remove the ‘click chests for slayer expirience’ and make it attack chickens/new NPC for expirience.
Training area? Dude spread em out a bit, add lots of different NPC’s, not just line them up all the same.
Don’t have shops right next to your PK areas.
